      "description": "Discover the freedom to build your Hill Country retreat on this scenic 8-acre homesite in Eden Ranch. With sweeping Hill Country views, sloping terrain, and a natural landscape of mature oaks and cedar, this property offers the perfect canvas for a custom home designed to take full advantage of the surrounding beauty.\n\nThe gently rolling topography creates ideal building opportunities for a home with elevated views, expansive patios, and outdoor living spaces that capture the sunrise and sunset over the Texas Hill Country. Electric is available and private wells are allowed, giving you flexibility as you design and build your dream property.\n\nLocated on paved Eden Ranch Drive, this acreage provides the privacy and elbow room buyers are searching for, while still being close to everything that makes Canyon Lake living special. Spend weekends boating, fishing, and enjoying nearby Canyon Lake and Guadalupe River recreation, or take a short drive to dining, shopping, and entertainment in New Braunfels and the surrounding Hill Country communities.\n\nWith no HOA, you'll enjoy greater freedom in how you design your property, while mobile and manufactured homes are restricted, helping preserve the character and quality of the surrounding acreage homesites.\n\nIf you've been searching for space, views, and the relaxed outdoorsy Hill Country lifestyle, this property is ready for your vision.",
